==Bundles==
Purple Mushroom is used in
* The {{Bundle|Field Research||y}}.
* one of the options for the {{Bundle|Exotic||y}} '''or''' the {{Bundle|Wild Medicine||y}}.

==Recipes==
Despite the numbers listed on the tooltip, the [[Life Elixir]] will fully restore [[Health]] to maximum regardless of how low it is.
