==Tailoring==
Purple Mushroom is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{name|Shirt099|link=Tailoring{{!}}Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a purple dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the purple dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*The Purple Mushroom may be randomly requested during any season at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|750}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.  Purple Mushroom will never be requested until you have reached the bottom of [[The Mines]].
*2-3 Purple Mushrooms may be requested by [[Catfish]], [[Octopus]], [[Rainbow Trout]], [[Spook Fish]], or [[Super Cucumber]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 5 to 7.

